tip.text: The ribs are awesome! I was never into ribs but Hard Rock Cafe changed my mind. 👍👍👍
The laksa from #01-33 is delicious. The taste of the gravy is well balanced. Not too spicy, not too lemak. It's the old school type of laksa. The tau pok is yummy! Good value at S$3.00.
The fried cockles with bits of sweet sticky yummy pork lard. So tasty! 👍
Bring your family here! Free beer for daddy, free ice cream for mummy and free toy for the little one. 👍
Pork chop rice is yummy! And if you need a refreshing drink on a hot day, go for the herbal tea. My favorite small bites - meat balls! So good!
